"ANU\n","anu\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##Print first character of a string variable.Print last character of a string variable."],"metadata":{"id":"tnGfj2uQ8b8b"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["a='anuharika'\n","print(\"first\",a[0])\n","print(\"last\",a[-2]) #from last there is no index 0\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"tY-ClzCU8lo_","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780414264888,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":20,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"e8c63ef9-9016-440a-cd66-786b8f3b5671"},"execution_count":54,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["first a\n","last k\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### User Input Variables"],"metadata":{"id":"C1nxjJFN9r0q"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["name=input(\"user name:\")\n","print(\"welcom\",name)\n","\n","age=int(input(\"user age:\"))\n","print(age)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"oovGWUBQ9voT","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780414569401,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":6193,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"b5049351-8aac-412d-a668-445821ba61ac"},"execution_count":57,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["user name:anu\n","welcom anu\n","user age:21\n","21\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["a=int(input(\"enter 1st num:\"))\n","b=int(input('enter 2nd num:'))\n","print(\"sum:\",a+b)\n","print('diff:',a-b)\n","print('product:',a*b)\n","print('division:',a/b)\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"Qt3YAAxz-JBo","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780414933922,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":3856,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"94a5bfdd-06d4-46a8-a080-9868862ee8e6"},"execution_count":64,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["enter 1st num:5\n","enter 2nd num:5\n","sum: 10\n","diff: 0\n","product: 25\n","division: 1.0\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["###Interview\n","\n","##What is a variable in Python?\n","\n","   -'is a memory location .it stores value from progaram\n","  -'no declaration needed it csn figure out automatically'\n","  -'Variables are called \"variable\" because their values can vary or change during the program'\n","\n","  Python is dynamically typed, so a variable can hold values of different data types at different times.\n","\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"jZgaxa-qAIEK"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["x = 10      # int\n","print(type(x))\n","\n","x = \"Hello\" # str\n","print(type(x))"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"XLSSHrSqIaQa","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780417146770,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":32,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"eb6b4ef5-73b4-482b-8229-749ecee867db"},"execution_count":72,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["<class 'int'>\n","<class 'str'>\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##What are the rules for naming variables?\n","  -allowed characters and _\n","  -cannot start with digit   1name\n","  -case-sensitive\n","  -no reserved keywords\n","          print,if ,true\n","  -no space/spaces/punctuations\n","         -,@,$,  can use: college_name"],"metadata":{"id":"VX0Gv54MD02K"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["These four are the most common built-in data types in Python. They tell Python what kind of value a variable is holding and what you can do with it.\n","\n","Here is the breakdown of the differences:\n","\n","1. int (Integer)\n","What it is: Whole numbers, both positive and negative, without any decimal points.\n","\n","Example: age = 21 or temperature = -5\n","\n","Use case: Counting things, indexing, or loops.\n","\n","2. float (Floating-point number)\n","What it is: Numbers that contain a decimal point or fractional part.\n","\n","Example: pi = 3.14 or salary = 45000.0\n","\n","Use case: Precise measurements, calculations, or percentages.\n","\n","3. str (String)\n","What it is: Text or a sequence of characters wrapped inside single quotes (') or double quotes (\").\n","\n","Example: name = 'Anu' or city = \"Korutla\"\n","\n","Use case: Storing words, messages, user inputs, or labels.\n","\n","4. bool (Boolean)\n","What it is: A logical value that can only ever be one of two things: True or False. (Note: Capitalization matters in Python!)\n","\n","Example: is_student = True\n","\n","Use case: Making decisions in code (like if/else statements) and checking if conditions are met."],"metadata":{"id":"MNWS3-ByFXIk"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Can a variable's datatype change in Python? Give an example.\n"],"metadata":{"id":"MSdL6dUPFivQ"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["x=10\n","y=x\n","x=20\n","print(y)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"jLOntGcgFlNI","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780416454153,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":27,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"630e1488-f03b-4b82-e17a-568eda746cfd"},"execution_count":66,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["10\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### mini assignment\n"],"metadata":{"id":"rsLJ7SeOGbsM"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["print(\"Employee Details\\n----------------------------------\")\n","print('Name   :  Anu')\n","print('Age    :  22')\n","print('City   :  Hyderabad')\n","print('Salary :  45000')\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"ATJXnwxRGwjd","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780417008493,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":32,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"c9715fec-3c0e-4733-8992-6390631e45b2"},"execution_count":71,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Employee Details\n","----------------------------------\n","Name   :  Anu\n","Age    :  22\n","City   :  Hyderabad\n","Salary :  45000\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## Rectangle Area"],"metadata":{"id":"KNGNUbtzIzJH"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["length=10.2\n","width=5.5\n","\n","area=length*width\n","print(\"area\",area)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"4zBiwzSXHtLN","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780417336659,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":28,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"3abed87f-95af-47bd-d391-ba4478cbc950"},"execution_count":73,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["area 56.099999999999994\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Temperature Converter\n","celsius = 37\n","fahrenheit = (celsius * 9/5) + 32\n","\n","# Clean and fixed f-string\n","print(f\"{celsius}°C is equal to {fahrenheit}°F\")"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"KSmlnCHNJfbM","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780417757276,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":33,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"8c482cd7-c6d0-422d-aab2-a00fbd5ee8ee"},"execution_count":78,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["37°C is equal to 98.6°F\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#avg\n","\n","maths=80\n","physics=90\n","science=78\n","\n","#total\n","total_marks=maths+physics+science\n","\n","#avg\n","avg_marks=total_marks/3\n","\n","print(f\"total_marks:{total_marks}\")\n","print(f\"avg_marks:{avg_marks}\")"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"HObnPw4cJwlO","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780418063653,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":35,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"ab9ae6c7-356c-4c07-9f34-6ad181b26142"},"execution_count":79,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["total_marks:248\n","avg_marks:82.66666666666667\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["# Take input for:\n","Student Name\n","Roll Number\n","Marks in 3 Subjects"],"metadata":{"id":"SsJ3XQ_JMjez"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["name=input('enter your name:')\n","roll=input(\"enter your roll number:\")\n","\n","sub1=int(input(\"enter sub1 marks:\"))\n","sub2=int(input(\"enter sub2 marks:\"))\n","sub3=int(input(\"enter sub2 marks:\"))\n","\n","total_marks=sub1+sub2+sub3\n","\n","avg_marks=total_marks/3\n","\n","print('========================')\n","print(f\"name: {name}\")\n","print(f\"roll num: {roll}\")\n","print(f\"total:{total_marks}\")\n","print(f\"avg:{avg_marks}\")\n","\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"JaUKPqeuMg5y","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780418916401,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":28577,"user":{"displayName":"Anu214","userId":"15186858036074631678"}},"outputId":"0161fc3a-3411-4418-d0b9-23aa93fa4350"},"execution_count":86,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["enter your name:anu\n","enter your roll number:f5\n","enter sub1 marks:90\n","enter sub2 marks:89\n","enter sub2 marks:70\n","========================\n","name: anu\n","roll num: f5\n","total:249\n","avg:83.0\n"]}]}]}